name: Catatan Belajar #02 - Seeking for The Truth
description:
Depicting the struggle of man to seek the truth, but the truth is always in front of the eye. Every person has a right way to do, to seek and accept.

It was about the struggle of acceptance and not about faith or devotion.

"Catatan Belajar" or "Study Notes" is a project to record the studied things as I am currently studying my religion again.
